The following is the list of goals that are expected for the Downtime Calculator:
1: Allow Multi-Account tracking of gold for campaigns
2: Track the History of the Accounts within the Campaign
3: Single button "Accrue Interest" for In game Month end
4: Automatically roll the d100 and apply the results Per account
5: Allow Interest to go to any account within the campaign--theirs or others
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The following are extended goals:
1: Allow for Multiple types of investments (Art, etc)
2: Single File Save Format
3: Meta-Display of all accounts on a single page.
4: Meta-Display of all investments for a single account
